{"ja512:0.1":"Jataka ","ja512:0.2":"Timsanipata ","ja512:0.3":"Kimchandavagga ","ja512:0.4":"2. Kumbhajataka ","ja512:1.1":"“Ko paturasi tidiva nabhamhi, ","ja512:1.2":"Obhasayam samvarim candimava; ","ja512:1.3":"Gattehi te rasmiyo niccharanti, ","ja512:1.4":"Saterata vijjurivantalikkhe. ","ja512:2.1":"So chinnavatam kamasi aghamhi, ","ja512:2.2":"Vehayasam gacchasi titthasi ca; ","ja512:2.3":"Iddhi nu te vatthukata subhavita, ","ja512:2.4":"Anaddhagunam api devatanam. ","ja512:3.1":"Vehayasam gammamagamma titthasi, ","ja512:3.2":"Kumbham kinathati yametamattham; ","ja512:3.3":"Ko va tuvam kissa va taya kumbho, ","ja512:3.4":"Akkhahi me brahmana etamattham”. ","ja512:4.1":"“Na sappikumbho napi telakumbho, ","ja512:4.2":"Na phanitassa na madhussa kumbho; ","ja512:4.3":"Kumbhassa vajjani anappakani, ","ja512:4.4":"Dose bahu kumbhagate sunatha. ","ja512:5.1":"Galeyya yam pitva pate papatam, ","ja512:5.2":"Sobbham guham candaniyoligallam; ","ja512:5.3":"Bahumpi bhunjeyya abhojaneyyam, ","ja512:5.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:6.1":"Yam pitva cittasmimanesamano, ","ja512:6.2":"Ahindati goriva bhakkhasadi; ","ja512:6.3":"Anathamano upagayati naccati ca, ","ja512:6.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:7.1":"Yam ve pivitva acelova naggo, ","ja512:7.2":"Careyya game visikhantarani; ","ja512:7.3":"Sammulhacitto ativelasayi, ","ja512:7.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:8.1":"Yam pitva utthaya pavedhamano, ","ja512:8.2":"Sisanca bahunca pacalayanto; ","ja512:8.3":"So naccati darukatallakova, ","ja512:8.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:9.1":"Yam ve pivitva aggidaddha sayanti, ","ja512:9.2":"Atho sigalehipi khaditase; ","ja512:9.3":"Bandham vadham bhogajanincupenti, ","ja512:9.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:10.1":"Yam pitva bhaseyya abhasaneyyam, ","ja512:10.2":"Sabhayamasino apetavattho; ","ja512:10.3":"Sammakkhito vantagato byasanno, ","ja512:10.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:11.1":"Yam ve pivitva ukkattho avilakkho, ","ja512:11.2":"Mameva sabba pathaviti manne; ","ja512:11.3":"Na me samo caturantopi raja, ","ja512:11.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:12.1":"Manatimana kalahani pesuni, ","ja512:12.2":"Dubbannini naggayini palayini; ","ja512:12.3":"Corana dhuttana gati niketo, ","ja512:12.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:13.1":"Iddhani phitani kulani assu, ","ja512:13.2":"Anekasahassadhanani loke; ","ja512:13.3":"Ucchinnadayajjakatanimaya, ","ja512:13.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:14.1":"Dhannam dhanam rajatam jatarupam, ","ja512:14.2":"Khettam gavam yattha vinasayanti; ","ja512:14.3":"Ucchedani vittavatam kulanam, ","ja512:14.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:15.1":"Yam ve pitva dittarupova poso, ","ja512:15.2":"Akkosati mataram pitaranca; ","ja512:15.3":"Sassumpi ganheyya athopi sunham, ","ja512:15.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:16.1":"Yam ve pitva dittarupava nari, ","ja512:16.2":"Akkosati sasuram samikanca; ","ja512:16.3":"Dasampi ganhe paricarakampi, ","ja512:16.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:17.1":"Yam ve pivitvana haneyya poso, ","ja512:17.2":"Dhamme thitam samanam brahmanam va; ","ja512:17.3":"Gacche apayampi tatonidanam, ","ja512:17.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:18.1":"Yam ve pivitva duccaritam caranti, ","ja512:18.2":"Kayena vacaya ca cetasa ca; ","ja512:18.3":"Nirayam vajanti duccaritam caritva, ","ja512:18.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:19.1":"Yam yacamana na labhanti pubbe, ","ja512:19.2":"Bahum hirannampi pariccajanta; ","ja512:19.3":"So tam pivitva alikam bhanati, ","ja512:19.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:20.1":"Yam ve pitva pesane pesiyanto, ","ja512:20.2":"Accayike karaniyamhi jate; ","ja512:20.3":"Atthampi so nappajanati vutto, ","ja512:20.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:21.1":"Hirimanapi ahirikabhavam, ","ja512:21.2":"Patum karonti madanaya matta; ","ja512:21.3":"Dhirapi santa bahukam bhananti, ","ja512:21.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:22.1":"Yam ve pitva ekathupa sayanti, ","ja512:22.2":"Anasaka thandiladukkhaseyyam; ","ja512:22.3":"Dubbanniyam ayasakyancupenti, ","ja512:22.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:23.1":"Yam ve pitva pattakhandha sayanti, ","ja512:23.2":"Gavo kutahatava na hi varuniya; ","ja512:23.3":"Vego narena susahoriva, ","ja512:23.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:24.1":"Yam manussa vivajjenti, ","ja512:24.2":"sappam ghoravisamiva; ","ja512:24.3":"Tam loke visasamanam, ","ja512:24.4":"ko naro patumarahati. ","ja512:25.1":"Yam ve pitva andhakavendaputta, ","ja512:25.2":"Samuddatire paricarayanta; ","ja512:25.3":"Upakkamum musalehannamannam, ","ja512:25.4":"Tassa punnam kumbhamimam kinatha. ","ja512:26.1":"Yam ve pitva pubbadeva pamatta, ","ja512:26.2":"Tidiva cuta sassatiya samaya; ","ja512:26.3":"Tam tadisam majjamimam niratthakam, ","ja512:26.4":"Janam maharaja katham piveyya. ","ja512:27.1":"Nayimasmim kumbhasmim dadhi va madhu va, ","ja512:27.2":"Evam abhinnaya kinahi raja; ","ja512:27.3":"Evanhimam kumbhagata maya te, ","ja512:27.4":"Akkhatarupam tava sabbamitta”. ","ja512:28.1":"“Na me pita va athavapi mata, ","ja512:28.2":"Etadisa yadisako tuvamsi; ","ja512:28.3":"Hitanukampi paramatthakamo, ","ja512:28.4":"Soham karissam vacanam tavajja. ","ja512:29.1":"Dadami te gamavarani panca, ","ja512:29.2":"Dasisatam satta gavamsatani; ","ja512:29.3":"Ajannayutte ca rathe dasa ime, ","ja512:29.4":"Acariyo hosi mamatthakamo”. ","ja512:30.1":"“Taveva dasisatamatthu raja, ","ja512:30.2":"Gama ca gavo ca taveva hontu; ","ja512:30.3":"Ajannayutta ca ratha taveva, ","ja512:30.4":"Sakkohamasmi tidasanamindo. ","ja512:31.1":"Mamsodanam sappipayasam bhunja, ","ja512:31.2":"Khadassu ca tvam madhumasapuve; ","ja512:31.3":"Evam tuvam dhammarato janinda, ","ja512:31.4":"Anindito saggamupehi thanan”ti. ","ja512:32.1":"Kumbhajatakam dutiyam. "}